 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>배포가 왜… 안되는거지…?</h3>\n<p>우선 github repository를 cloudflare Pages에서 불러와 아래와 같이 설정값을 입력하여 배포를 시도하였습니다. <code>Vite</code>는 따로 없었기에 설정하지 않았고, 빌드 명령어와 더불어 <code>NODE_VERSION</code>을 환경 변수로 추가하였습니다.</p>\n<br/>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 708px; margin: 0.25rem 0; padding: 0;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/f97d7/cloudflareVariable.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 36.72316384180791%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAHCAIAAACHqfpvAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAAj0lEQVR42o2OUQ+DIBCD/f9/02UmOwacHuCB4OoSfRS/p3JpaYcYIzOHEPYTVQ1/9h6DyGKds9Zebs3qvReRfnhmJjLOuVX1bF6t/dZa+2EUojbGcLlLKeF4tiezxRhDROx52zYkc87lASg7wq9xfE8TzzM0huCjDxGE3JJSGo6R8C0LGjG0tYaLQveotf4Am1uZ6VO9rJgAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"cloudflareVariable\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/d65de/cloudflareVariable.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/ad6ca/cloudflareVariable.png 177w,\n/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/16bd5/cloudflareVariable.png 354w,\n/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/d65de/cloudflareVariable.png 708w,\n/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/3e86e/cloudflareVariable.png 1062w,\n/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/c6e0f/cloudflareVariable.png 1416w,\n/static/c84b34a9d0364708d9302b277a61e58a/f97d7/cloudflareVariable.png 2000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 708px